{"tid":2410206,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金所炫拍古裝穿韓服拜年被說「文化偷竊」？中國網友湧入IG引中韓論戰！","createTime":"2021-02-16T12:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T13:14:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc4a284e00464f4d4bfb0734900f913b1eff683","tid":2410206,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561194_1613434951.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561194_1613434951.webp&h=08293290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n農曆新年有不少韓星在自己的SNS上向粉絲傳遞祝福，近日在拍攝新作品《月升之江》的女演員金所炫，也在拍戲之際向粉絲賀年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561198_1613434943.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561198_1613434943.webp&h=1a2b4cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過前幾日他的文章一PO出，立刻引起了許多中國網友湧入，除了以「Happy Chinese New Year」洗版之外，更直接留言：「不要偷中國的服飾」、「謝謝你幫我們宣傳漢服」等留言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561197_1613434939.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561197_1613434939.webp&h=1146ad05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片中所炫穿著的是這次作品《月升之江》中的韓服，也沒有任何提到「中韓」的字眼，中國網友無端引起的論戰，讓韓網友看不下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561199_1613435001.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561199_1613435001.webp&h=b8b98d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓網友直呼：「那些人是不是瘋了？」、「無論如何這就是我們的電視劇、我們的服裝、我們的文化！不要再嫉妒心發作了！」、「不要傷害無辜的所炫」等留言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561200_1613434947.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561200_1613434947.webp&h=594cecd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這次中國主動引起的戰爭，讓韓網友們匪夷所思，也更加深了兩國網友之間的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561196_1613434936.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561196_1613434936.webp&h=ab985992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實上所炫不是第一個捲入「中韓文化」之戰的韓國藝人，舉凡偶像NCT、BLACKPINK、(G)I-DLE等都曾因為身著韓服或是以「Happy Chinese New Year」的祝賀語，都被網友拿出來討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/16/550_1561195_1613434924.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F550_1561195_1613434924.webp&h=c50557e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《月升之江》改編自小說《平岡公主》，講述夢想成為王、並利用溫達感情的平岡公主，與像傻瓜般只懂犧牲的溫達之間的淒美愛情故事，將於2月15日首播。"},{"pid":"01ebe79e1edaa86d2e97c64f75b0fad54ff56479","tid":2410206,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:01:36.000Z","msg":"所以防火牆對全世界都係德政，最好再加強一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fbaa124f40d11998c0aa67707cb3bc1689ad29","tid":2410206,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90089baedc37b8a964ff7c5ac905939102aa25b4","tid":2410206,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01ebe79e1edaa86d2e97c64f75b0fad54ff56479","tid":2410206,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:01:36.000Z","msg":"所以防火牆對全世界都係德政，最好再加強一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"唔拆牆點加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}